From:RockyBalboa
Value Investing: I put some fun money into a famous company - Beate Uhse
(DE:USE). Stock heavily discounted trading at E1.30 to 1.35. The company might
be in a crisis but its stuff will always be useful for a whole lot of folks.
Currently a secondary with rights is placed which depresses the stock price
